{"tid":432520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好多謝林鄭今次份施政報告，好多利民政策","createTime":"2017-10-11T14:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T05:26:31.000Z","uid":33307,"like":259,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0ecf29fb052fe56eaf2617207bb0c1cf8005e1c0","tid":432520,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n回一舊水車費比我？<br />\nd錢全部都係納稅人俾架<br />\n派？邊撚到派呀？<br />\n冇納稅？我屌你老母啦<br />\n就係比你辦仆街日日吸血先冇份納稅<br />\n咪撚以為自己好偉大<br />\n你班官成家都係市民養<br />\n香港今日呢個地步係你地自己做成<br />\n咪撚講咩熱廚房<br />\n咪撚怪人要搞獨立<br />\n全部都係你地自己種既果<br />\n香港人冇欠你地架屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd992ea8b0e5042e3be0be66071cd38cf83ecd7e","tid":432520,"uid":33307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d50fc8bd92845ece4782d1c16ff7f37ad3f6647","tid":432520,"uid":47359,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"借個位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOct 11 近期活躍五毛<br />\n1三色貓<br />\n2法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國<br />\n3十卜ching<br />\n4侵B<br />\n5返六日唔撚易<br />\n6國語好手<br />\n7bb chu<br />\n8Redbaron<br />\n9newlife<br />\n10優美開始"},{"pid":"cce0b3a5a353d05f56ca909acc5e0db208cf6bc5","tid":432520,"uid":33307,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"再屌柒埋佢個首置盤<br />\n屌佢老母<br />\n首置盤=居屋白表<br />\n綠置居=居屋綠表<br />\n有幾撚石破天驚呀？<br />\n改年左個名炸？<br />\n咪又係果d屋<br />\n冇地就冇地啦垃圾<br />\n搞咁多花臣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed61290dbc26179fa9e5c8a76c89af28eac58cbf","tid":432520,"uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy